c: 10
v: 27
t: "Ne balia bakhola amabii, omurungo kwamabii nilibi lienesa liabarirungwa, ne balinyoola tsisoni, Ne balibula ulia unyala okhubalinda khushinyasio shia Nyasaye. Obweni bwabu buliba shinga bufunikhwekhwo ebilo bieshilima eshikhongo. Abo nibo Abandu bomumulilo balikhalamwo tsinyanga tsiosi"